announcements: Participation is 100% voluntary, and the results will be used as a resource in our ward employment efforts to assist those who have been affected by difficult work situations. This information will be kept highly confidential, and will only ever be viewed by a select few members of the Ward Council and our Ward Employment Specialist. This information will never be made public or distributed in any way, shape, or form. We invite all ward members to prayerfully consider the blessings that will come as we help one another to navigate the waters of employment.
